@startuml fuel_battery_state_to_obc_charge_power_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Fuel Battery State To OBC Charge Power Signal Flow\n(fuel/battery state + vehicle state -> OBC state, plug state, and charge power)

participant "Fuel/battery bus" as FuelBat #F4F7FB
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #E8F0FE
participant "OBC\non-board charger owner" as OBC #E8F7E8
participant "OBC state bus" as ObcBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\ncharge readers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== OBC Inputs ==

FuelBat -> OBC : frmFuelBatteryStateMsg\nBatterySoc / ChargingState
Veh -> OBC : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
activate OBC
OBC -> OBC : inputStale / vehicleInputStale\nlease checks
OBC -> OBC : if stale then\nbatterySoc = 50 / chargingState = 0
OBC -> OBC : vehicleParked =\n(driveState == 0) or (chargingState > 0)
OBC -> OBC : acPlugState =\nchargingState in {1,3} and vehicleParked
OBC -> OBC : obcState = 3 when paused,\n2 when active AC charge, else 0
OBC -> OBC : chargePowerKw =\n(100 - batterySoc) / 2 under active charge
note right of OBC
Representative gating inputs
- BatterySoc
- ChargingState
- gDriveState
end note

== OBC Publish ==

OBC -> ObcBus : frmObcStateMsg\nObcState / AcPlugState / ChargePowerKw
note right of OBC
Representative outputs
- ObcState
- AcPlugState
- ChargePowerKw
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

ObcBus -> Obs : OBC visibility /\nCPC and charging observers
deactivate OBC

note over FuelBat, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Fuel/battery and vehicle state reach OBC
2. OBC evaluates plug posture and active charging state
3. OBC derives effective charge power from SOC gap
4. OBC publishes charger state for downstream charging consumers
end note

@enduml
